hese conditions fail. In such cases, the\ninformation capacity (the maximum number of mutually distinguishable states) of\na composite is greater than the product of the capacities of its constituents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2016 03:07:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Dec 2019 15:05:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 5 Nov 2020 02:09:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
