ted luminosity. We conclude that in all considered cases the signal is\nbelow the background or/and below the threshold set by statistics although some\ntension can be seen.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2016 13:03:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-01"}
