ns from a mobile impurity model, and clarify the relation of the\neffective field theory parameters to the Bethe Ansatz solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2016 14:43:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2016 16:47:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-10"}
